  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTIONS 75-75-101, 75-75-105, 75-75-109, 75-75-115 AND 75-75-117, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REMOVE WRESTLING MATCHES FROM UNDER THE SUPERVISION OF THE MISSISSIPPI ATHLETIC COMMISSION; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 75-75-123, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH EXEMPTS COLLEGE, UNIVERSITY AND HIGH SCHOOL BOXING, SPARRING AND WRESTLING MATCHES FROM THE JURISDICTION OF THE MISSISSIPPI ATHLETIC COMMISSION, FOR THE PURPOSES OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
